data.description:
Welcome home to this updated 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home on a corner lot! Sellers offering $2000 towards a carpet allowance! The home is pre inspected and comes with a home warranty. This home offers a nice sized backyard with a playset and shed. There are several updates to this home including, all new siding in 2022, new roof in 2022, 3rd driveway and updated driveway in 2023, stone added to the exterior of the home in 2022. The updates continue with new LVP flooring on the main level installed in 2022, a newer furnace installed in 2021, a newer water heater installed in 2021, a new AC unit installed in 2022, a new dryer replaced in 2022 and new sewage pipes in 2023. Come on over and check this home out!
Items Reserved: Refrigerator in garage, deep freezer in garage, fridge in primary bedroom and shelving in the basement utility room
